                <![CDATA[DeFi 利率不敵傳統金融？解析 RWA 如何為 DeFi 帶來新機遇]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">量化對沖機構 Alphabeth Capital 分析師撰文指出 DeFi 利率不敵傳統金融的事實，但也表明自己對 RWA 資產的看好，認為 RWA 在未來將會是 DeFi 中最大類別之一。</p><p><a href="https://twitter.com/DeFi_Made_Here/status/1706342170603798799?s=20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">原文連結</a></p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/rwa-to-be-the-biggest-category-in-defi#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-65139969d4227"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-65139969d4227"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/rwa-to-be-the-biggest-category-in-defi/#%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95_DeFi_TVL%E3%80%81%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A%E5%B9%A3%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E9%A9%9F%E9%99%8D%EF%BC%9F" title="為何 DeFi TVL、穩定幣市值驟降？">為何 DeFi TVL、穩定幣市值驟降？</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/rwa-to-be-the-biggest-category-in-defi/#%E7%8F%BE%E5%AF%A6%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2_RWA_%E6%88%90_DeFi_%E6%95%91%E6%98%9F%EF%BC%9F" title="現實世界資產 (RWA) 成 DeFi 救星？">現實世界資產 (RWA) 成 DeFi 救星？</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/rwa-to-be-the-biggest-category-in-defi/#%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95_RWA_%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%8A%E6%96%BC_DeFi%EF%BC%9F" title="為何 RWA 有益於 DeFi？">為何 RWA 有益於 DeFi？</a><ul class="ez-toc-list-level-3"><li class="ez-toc-heading-level-3"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4" href="https://abmedia.io/rwa-to-be-the-biggest-category-in-defi/#Flux_Finance" title="Flux Finance">Flux Finance</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5" href="https://abmedia.io/rwa-to-be-the-biggest-category-in-defi/#Pendle_Finance" title="Pendle Finance">Pendle Finance</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95_DeFi_TVL%E3%80%81%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A%E5%B9%A3%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E9%A9%9F%E9%99%8D%EF%BC%9F"></span><strong>為何 DeFi TVL、穩定幣市值驟降？</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>分析師 DeFi Made Here (以下稱 DMH) 指出，DeFi 的總 TVL、穩定幣市值驟降，是因為 DeFi 利率慘敗傳統金融，大家在「無風險」的美債收益幾乎是 Aave 上的兩倍之多。</p><p><img class="size-full wp-image-79752 aligncenter" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/F64lKQkaoAARyFp.png?resize=834%2C430&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="834" height="430" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/F64lKQkaoAARyFp.png?w=834&amp;ssl=1 834w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/F64lKQkaoAARyFp.png?resize=300%2C155&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/F64lKQkaoAARyFp.png?resize=600%2C309&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/F64lKQkaoAARyFp.png?resize=768%2C396&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 834px) 100vw, 834px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E7%8F%BE%E5%AF%A6%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2_RWA_%E6%88%90_DeFi_%E6%95%91%E6%98%9F%EF%BC%9F"></span><strong>現實世界資產 (RWA) 成 DeFi 救星？</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>DMH 認為，將 RWA 引入至區塊鏈能幫助 DeFi 維持局面。</p><p>據 DefiLlama，RWA 目前市值約 24 億美元，而美國銀行更曾預測，RWA 在 5 到 15 年的時間內將達到 16 兆美元，</p><p>只不過目前光是波場 TRON 的 RWA 產品「stUSDT」就佔了 18 億美元，幣安的 RWA 報告也指出，stUSDT 在 RWA 貢獻的高 TVL 功不可沒。</p><p>回顧報導：</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://abmedia.io/tron-rwa-product-stusdt-introduction" target="_blank" rel="noopener">stUSDT：孫宇晨最新支持 RWA 力作介紹！首日吸金超 2200 萬 USDT</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://abmedia.io/binance-rwa-report-202307" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2030 年現實世界資產市值將達 16 兆美元，幣安盤點今年 RWA 進展</a></p></li></ul><p><img class="size-full wp-image-79753 aligncenter" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2023-09-26-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.47.38.png?resize=1582%2C485&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1582" height="485" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 4.47.38.png?w=1582&amp;ssl=1 1582w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 4.47.38.png?resize=300%2C92&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 4.47.38.png?resize=1024%2C314&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 4.47.38.png?resize=600%2C184&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 4.47.38.png?resize=768%2C235&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 4.47.38.png?resize=1536%2C471&amp;ssl=1 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95_RWA_%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%8A%E6%96%BC_DeFi%EF%BC%9F"></span><strong>為何 RWA 有益於 DeFi？</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><h3><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Flux_Finance"></span><a href="https://twitter.com/FluxDeFi" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Flux Finance</strong></a><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h3><p>DMH 解釋，RWA 將鏈下的收益帶到了鏈上，並允許其它專案利用 DeFi 的可組合性，在 RWA 上再另行打造產品，以獲得更高收益。</p><p>例如用戶能在 Flux Finance 上抵押代幣化美債，或開槓桿。</p><div class="N54PNb BToiNc cvP2Ce" data-snc="ih6Jnb_ZvFUZe"><div class="kb0PBd cvP2Ce jGGQ5e" data-snf="x5WNvb" data-snhf="0"><div class="yuRUbf"><div><h3 class="LC20lb MBeuO DKV0Md"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Pendle_Finance"></span><a href="https://twitter.com/pendle_fi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pendle Finance</a><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h3></div></div></div></div><p>Pendle Finance 則為用戶提供了固定收益及交易機會。</p><p>用戶能透過 sDAI、fUSDC 來保證債券到期時的最終收益。</p><p>若用戶不想投機收益率，想獲得固定的收益，也能在 Pendle 上提供流動性，獲得穩定幣市場中最高的收益率之一。</p><p><img class="size-full wp-image-79773 aligncenter" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2023-09-26-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885.44.52.png?resize=1270%2C311&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1270" height="311" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 5.44.52.png?w=1270&amp;ssl=1 1270w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 5.44.52.png?resize=300%2C73&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 5.44.52.png?resize=1024%2C251&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 5.44.52.png?resize=600%2C147&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/截圖-2023-09-26-下午 5.44.52.png?resize=768%2C188&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>此外，RWA 已佔據 Pendle 總 TVL 的 13.6% (1.5 億美元有 2,000 萬美元)，隨著更多 RWA 與鏈上整合，作者認為 RWA 的 TVL 將顯著上升。</p><p>未來，RWA 市場可能成為 DeFi 最大的類別之一，而正為 RWA 打造基礎設施的專案也或許將大幅受益於此。</p>
]]>
